ocaranfil/bitrefill/minipanel-blank-night-2\npnpm dev --port 3099 &\nDEV_PID=$!\n# wait for server\ncurl -s --retry 15 --retry-connrefused --retry-delay 2 -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http://localhost:3099/trends\n```\n\nNote: `pnpm dev` starts both ClickHouse and Next.js via concurrently. Check if ClickHouse binary exists. If not, Next.js may fail to start.\n\nCheck the rendered HTML of `/trends` for:\n- Contains text \"Trends\"\n- Contains `data-testid=\"trends-controls\"`\n- Contains `data-testid=\"trend-chart\"`\n\nKill server after checks:\n```bash\nkill $DEV_PID 2>/dev/null; kill $(lsof -ti:3099) 2>/dev/null; true\n```\n\n## Sprint contract criteria to verify\n\nFrom `features/F22-plan.md`:\n- [ ] `pnpm test` (vitest run) → 0 failures\n- [ ] `pnpm lint` (biome check) → exit 0\n- [ ] `pnpm typecheck` (tsc --noEmit) → exit 0\n- [ ] `pnpm build` (next build) → exit 0\n- [ ] File `src/components/trends/useTrends.ts` exists and exports a `useTrends` function\n- [ ] File `src/components/trends/TrendsControls.tsx` exists and exports a named `TrendsControls` component\n- [ ] File `src/components/TrendChart.tsx` exists and exports a named `TrendChart` component\n- [ ] File `src/app/trends/page.tsx` exists and imports `TrendChart`\n- [ ] File `src/app/trends/page.tsx` exists and imports `TrendsControls`\n- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/trends` → response contains `Trends`\n- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/trends` → response contains `data-testid=\"trends-controls\"` or the controls container\n- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/trends` → response contains `data-testid=\"trend-chart\"` or the chart container\n\n## Integration tests to write\n\nThe plan identifies these as integration gaps:\n- HTTP check for GET `/trends` rendering the full page — requires dev server\n- Chart rendering with actual Recharts components\n- Full end-to-end flow (seed data → select event → verify chart shows data)\n\nIf Playwright is available (`playwright_tests/` directory exists), write a Playwright test at `playwright_tests/trends.spec.ts` that:\n1. Navigates to `/trends`\n2. Verifies the page title contains \"Trends\"\n3. Verifies the controls container is visible (data-testid=\"trends-controls\")\n4. Verifies the chart container is visible (data-testid=\"trend-chart\")\n\nCheck if Playwright is configured first by looking at `playwright.config.ts` or `playwright_tests/`.\n\n## Eval file output\n\nWrite `features/F22-eval-1.md` with this structure:\n\n```markdown\n# F22 Eval Sprint 1 — 2026-04-15\n\n## Tests written\n\n- <test file> — what criteria it covers\n\n## Sprint contract results\n| Criterion | Expected | Actual | Pass |\n|-----------|----------|--------|------|\n| ... | | | |\n\n## Score: X/10\n\n## Verdict: APPROVED / NEEDS_WORK\n\n## Feedback for next sprint\n(only if NEEDS_WORK)\n\n| Criterion | Error | File:Line | Action |\n|-----------|-------|-----------|--------|\n\n## Notes\n```\n\nBe objective and skeptical. Do not trust the generator's self-evaluation. Verify each criterion yourself.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21943,"cache_read_input_tokens":11937,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":21943},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"38862b96-3a4a-408b-a2fa-59c5b33b2701","uuid":"2a04ee3b-bb45-45e1-a1fb-0dbab664c66a"}
